{
  "texts": [
    "We comprehensively assess 11 LLMs, including API-based models and open-source models.",
    "The API-based models include GPT series (OpenAI, 2023).",
    "The open-source models include Llama-2 (Touvron et al., 2023), Llama-3, Mistral (Jiang et al., 2023), and Vicuna (Chiang et al., 2023) series.",
    "See Table 9 in Appendix F.3 for model details including version and link.",
    "And complete experimental settings including hyperparameters and costs are in Appendix F."
  ]
}